Subject: [PATCH 41/41] Update coredns/corefile-migration to support 1.12.4

New EKS-D releases for 1-29 to 1-34 branches ships with coredns 1.12.4. The corefile-migration package with release version 1.0.28 supports 1.12.4. Temporarily ovewriting the version
to point to the latest release 1.0.28. The patch can be removed once the package has been bumped in upstream capi.

Without this change, capi's webhook will deny a cluster spec with coredns 1.12.4 with the following error:
`invalid: spec.kubeadmConfigSpec.clusterConfiguration.dns.imageTag: Forbidden: cannot migrate CoreDNS up to '1.12.4' from '1.12.3'`
